#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/consul.md:204
msgid "Connection defaults automatically add `x-consul-token`, `dc`, and `timeout_ms` when they are configured and not overridden by the request."
